{"tid":740050,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"當年狼人咁紅，點解Avalon無乜人玩咁？","createTime":"2018-07-12T14:16:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T17:26:00.000Z","uid":194519,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"48a3507f3ec58780c6462ffaa29495022dc00c2f","tid":740050,"uid":194519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T14:16:19.000Z","msg":"我覺得Avalon正好多，狼人早死悶全場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae892c438810bfd7530d04069b31d0aeaadbbb1c","tid":740050,"uid":194519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T15:11:01.000Z","msg":"無人玩到無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aba49c5ed9658c7da58ae93ab7cf1e745d3dbdd","tid":740050,"uid":74339,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T15:14:34.000Z","msg":"勁好玩 但狼人易學易明好多"},{"pid":"10ff8ed3c514629c3f6bab7690e6ab53d7e8f5b2","tid":740050,"uid":141869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T15:15:15.000Z","msg":"只係聽過冇玩過,樓主介紹下?"},{"pid":"2a8fe54c79643f52bd7ae4d3309073e950a59b48","tid":740050,"uid":194519,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"10ff8ed3c514629c3f6bab7690e6ab53d7e8f5b2","tid":740050,"uid":141869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T15:15:15.000Z","msg":"只係聽過冇玩過,樓主介紹下?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T15:29:17.000Z","msg":"Avalon 故事背景講亞瑟王死後，佢嘅部下受命將佢復活。<br />\n<br />\n但當中有二五仔想整死亞瑟王，於是個遊戲就要搵啲二五仔出來。<br />\n<br />\n狼人有個大壞處係，早死嘅人玩足全場手機，Avalon所有人由頭玩到尾，無人會一早出局，投入感大增。<br />\n<br />\n部份角色有特殊能力，忠臣陣營最強係梅林，知晒所有壞人身份，但不能打太出，因為壞人如果估中邊個係梅林，就可以刺殺佢獲勝。<br />\n<br />\n壞人其中一個角色叫莫甘娜，可以扮自己係梅林引導全場。<br />\n<br />\n要分真假梅林就靠好人嘅派西維爾，如果佢分錯就好易令其他好人陷入困局，迫梅林現身帶隊。<br />\n<br />\n好有策略，好考演技，總之好好玩！"},{"pid":"e1af1f001f6090bd6d2eef755a2834ee711c078a","tid":740050,"uid":194519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0aba49c5ed9658c7da58ae93ab7cf1e745d3dbdd","tid":740050,"uid":74339,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T15:14:34.000Z","msg":"勁好玩 但狼人易學易明好多"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T15:30:28.000Z","msg":"我有班朋友個個星期玩幾個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"983b4855406295ae75814b1c9c6cd54dd4cd16b2","tid":740050,"uid":74339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1af1f001f6090bd6d2eef755a2834ee711c078a","tid":740050,"uid":194519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0aba49c5ed9658c7da58ae93ab7cf1e745d3dbdd","tid":740050,"uid":74339,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T15:14:34.000Z","msg":"勁好玩 但狼人易學易明好多"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T15:30:28.000Z","msg":"我有班朋友個個星期玩幾個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T15:32:14.000Z","msg":"係咪Avalon 預埋我得唔得"},{"pid":"aa1f1221187f379593e35a5c23201139c8f9340d","tid":740050,"uid":173349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e1af1f001f6090bd6d2eef755a2834ee711c078a","tid":740050,"uid":194519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0aba49c5ed9658c7da58ae93ab7cf1e745d3dbdd","tid":740050,"uid":74339,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T15:14:34.000Z","msg":"勁好玩 但狼人易學易明好多"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T15:30:28.000Z","msg":"我有班朋友個個星期玩幾個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T15:32:22.000Z","m